SELECT
    ap.db_actpsn_ludate AS ludate,
    ci.db_cifact_cifkey AS custid,
    ap.db_actpsn_zipno1 AS zipno1,
    ap.db_actpsn_zipno2 AS zipno2,
    ap.db_actpsn_addr   AS addr
FROM
    botsrdb.db_actpsn_dds ap
    LEFT JOIN botsrdb.db_cifact_dds ci ON ci.db_cifact_actno = ap.db_actpsn_actno
WHERE
        ap.db_actpsn_ludate = :batchDate
    AND ap.db_actpsn_actno != 0
    AND ci.db_cifact_cifkey IS NOT NULL
    AND ap.db_actpsn_ludate >= 880100
    AND ci.db_cifact_actaddr != 0
UNION ALL
SELECT
    ac.db_actcmp_ludate AS ludate,
    ci.db_cifact_cifkey AS custid,
    ac.db_actcmp_zipno1 AS zipno1,
    ac.db_actcmp_zipno2 AS zipno2,
    ac.db_actcmp_addr   AS addr
FROM
    botsrdb.db_actcmp_dds ac
    LEFT JOIN botsrdb.db_cifact_dds ci ON ci.db_cifact_actno = ac.db_actcmp_actno
WHERE
        ac.db_actcmp_ludate = :batchDate
    AND ac.db_actcmp_actno != 0
    AND ci.db_cifact_cifkey IS NOT NULL
    AND ac.db_actcmp_ludate >= 880100
    AND ci.db_cifact_actaddr != 0
ORDER BY　custid　ASC , ludate DESC
